Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehi! Non dirmi che Hideomi, in realtà...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma ti pare!\N L'ora del decesso stimata è...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'è eccome, il modo per farlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimmi, Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai mai... ucciso qualcuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.74,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Ma che diamine?!
